Summary: Explains the "Spread" parameter in the ParticleProcessMaterial for 2D particles.
Spread: This parameter is the angle in degrees which will be randomly added in either direction to the base Direction. A spread of 180 will emit in all directions (+/- 180). For spread to do anything the "Initial Velocity" parameter must be greater than 0.
---CHUNK---
